  m_text: "Ever wished you could decorate rooms your way? Now you can!\n\nThe long-awaited Room Customizer feature has officially launched!\nMix and match wallpapers, flooring, furniture, and quirky decorations to make every guest's stay unforgettable.\n\nDon't forget: customized rooms increase guest satisfaction and boost your hotel rating. Try it out!"
